fields.form_description:
In addition to celebrating IEEE Day 2023, the IEEE NSU Student Branch- INSB brings its “IEEE Day 2023 Membership Renewal Campaign” program, starting on 15th October 2023. This program will open the way to an exclusive platform where INSB members can renew their membership for 2024, explore exciting benefits, and engage with fellow IEEE enthusiasts. 

Renew your IEEE Membership and other societies and affinity groups subscriptions with us to continue developing your career, accessing essential networking opportunities, and receiving other exclusive IEEE benefits for the calendar year of 2024!

fields.group_name: IEEE NSU Power and Energy Society Student Branch Chapter
fields.page_title: IEEE NSU Power & Energy Society Student Branch Chapter
fields.about_description: IEEE NSU PES Student Branch Chapter is a technical sub-unit of one or more IEEE Societies. We thrive to provide scientific and engineering information on electric power and energy for the betterment of society, and the preferred professional development source of its members. We are highly active with our research activities. IEEE NSU PES Student Branch Chapter has ranked 5th in the Asia Pacific [IEEE Region 10] (16th globally by score) as an IEEE PES High Performing Student Branch Chapter 2020. One of the missions is to contribute to the field of Power and Energy with innovation and implementation of advanced technological ideas.
fields.mission_description:
-Active contribution with innovation and implementation of advanced technological ideas in the field of Power and Energy for the betterment of society.
-To become a part of IEEE PES High Performing Student Branch Chapter Program along with providing the platform enriched of preferred professional development resources for our members following 5 pillars of PES.
fields.vision_description:
-To advance global participation among enthusiastic volunteers with educating the future engineering leaders experiencing industry activity and research trends in addition to practicing student leadership following the IEEE communities.
-To provide technical and scientific information about advancements in the field of electrical power and energy to create and innovate for the future professional development of its members as well as engineering students with creating values for society with Humanitarian activities following UN SDG protocols.
fields.what_is_this_description: The Power and Energy Society(PES) provides the world’s largest forum to share the latest technological developments in the electric power industry, to guide the development and construction of equipment and systems, and to educate industry members and the general public and their employers – get substantial benefits from being involved with this unique and outstanding association.
fields.why_join_it:
Benefits of Membership in the IEEE Power & Energy Society Include:

  • You will get free subscription to PES award-winning Power & Energy magazine
  • Digital subscription to Electrification magazine is totally free here.
  • Free entrance to over 1000 technical reports, video, tutorials, and presentations on the PES Resource Center
  • You will get free membership in your local PES chapter
  • You will get discounts on dozens of PES sponsored or co-sponsored conferences and meetings not only in your region but also all around the world.
  • Discounts on technical tutorials.
  • Discount membership rate in five PES and four Sister society peer-reviewed technology journals
  • Get hours of continuing education unit or professional development by taking part in our general talk series.
  • Access to lots of live and archived technical and professional development webinars
  • There are many benefits to IEEE membership. Learn more here.
fields.what_activites_it_has: We host many events, seminars, workshops, Tech-talks and weekly meetings throughout the year on various topics within industry application. It helps the members to gather more knowledge about Robotics and Automation. Also, the members and participants get the chance to learn new skills and develop those skills by participating in events.
fields.how_to_join:
Joining IEEE and PES is easy. To join PES you must be an IEEE member first. Once you become an IEEE member, you can join PES easily. PES membership is only US$35 per year.

 The PES membership has more than 38,000 industry professionals, academics and students with a general interest in the electric power industry. To join pes the information are given below:

  • JOIN NOW!
  • Update Your IEEE Membership
  • Make the Most of Your PES Membership
  • Access Membership Benefits & Orientation Webinar Slides
  • PES Members and Authors Downloads

fields.title: Feelings About IEEE NSU Student Branch
fields.short_description: I joined IEEE in 2022 in the fall semester of NSU. I am lucky that I am a member of this organization. Because I have learned many technical things and so on. I can also learn about research work.
fields.description:
I joined IEEE in 2022 in the fall semester of NSU. I am lucky that I am a member of this organization. Because I have learned many technical things and so on. I can also learn about research work.

I have attended many programs and workshops of IEEE. They are:

  • Currents of Opportunity (Research avenues, Higher education strategies,, and Industry insights)

  • Seminar on IEEE membership perks.

  • Recent trends in 3D point cloud objected recognition.

  • Workshop on guided project series: powering

    microcontrollers using solar energy.

  • Workshop on Python, NumPy & Matplotlib for data

    analytics.

  • IEEE Day celebration.

  • GitHub Basic 2.0: Building your coding portfolio

  • IoT workshop

  • Technical visit at a cyber-physical systems research lab

I learned many things from these programs. I have average knowledge of Python. After attending the workshop my inspiration increased to build my advanced Python skills. Besides, when I attend the IOT and powering microcontrollers using solar energy workshop, I can learn technical skills. But I should be more practice and attend this type of program more. Then I can be skilled up. I can also know higher study and research scope abroad. I hope the IEEE NSU Student Branch will arrange more advanced programs than past programs. The branch counselor Saif Ahmed sir is very helpful. I am not a specially responsible member of IEEE. I am only a general member. I am trying to be a responsible part of IEEE.

fields.about_ieee: Since 1963, IEEE(Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers) is a large professional association for engineers. Its corporate office is in New York City at United States and its headquarter is located at Piscataway, New Jersey, United States. This  association focuses to develop Electrical Electronic and Technical sites, Computer Science and Engineering sites and finally the Telecommunications sites. This is the world wide association for all engineers now a days.
fields.community_description: Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) is the largest world wide professional association for engineering sites.  IEEE starts with 150,000 members(93% from US) group which is now extended with over 400,000 members from 160 countries, with the U.S. based membership no longer constituting a majority. It has the biggest community with a huge number of members and workers. There are huge numbers of Technical Societies , Technical councils and Technical Committees under IEEE. The IEEE community is like a family with so many heartiest peoples. To know more about this
fields.start_with_ieee_description: Who doesn’t wanna gain knowledge by experiencing something new and exciting!! If you wanna explore your life in a whole new way then IEEE is the best association for you. It will give you thousands of platforms and growing activities by which you can prepare yourself with a presentable way of thinking. If  you are interested to experience and to gain knowledge about the unknown mysterious techniques and inventions of science and Technology, then start with IEEE. fields.event_description:
Wondering how to boost revenues and to choose the right tech stack?

In today’s date web development has grabbed a lot of attention and there’s no doubt that the demand for creative web applications in today’s industry is running at a skyrocketing speed. But not all web applications have a seamless user experience. MERN Stack is one of the fastest web development processes which offers a single programming language to drastically simplify the entire development process.
MERN stack is a collection of robust and powerful technologies such as MongoDB, React, Express, NodeJS, used to develop web applications, interactive front-end, back-end, with full database. It is a user-friendly stack of technology that is basically a JavaScript framework for building dynamic websites and applications.

With an effort to deliver the experience about this simple and efficient web development process IEEE North South University Women In Engineering Affinity Group in collaboration with Shikhbe Shobai is going to offer a seminar in MERN Stack development namely “Acquaint with MERN Stack, Aspire Your Skill.”

We feel extremely fortunate that our esteemed speaker Tahsin Shahriar will compile all the things that one needs to know about MERN Stack Development. He majored in computer science and engineering from East West University and he is currently working as a freelance software developer and full stack web developer not only that he is also a mentor at Shikhbe Shobai. He will give you an extensive knowledge about the software development framework guide and will also cover popular technologies and frameworks.

By the end of the webinar, you will have skills, experience and confidence to dive into a career in web development.
And guess what!! The registration fee is absolutely free for all. Don’t forget to mark your calendars and join our webinar to unlock your skills in web development.
